<div class="answer-head">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730"
class="zm-item-link-avatar"
href="/people/kaiserwang730">
<img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg"
class="zm-list-avatar"
data-source="http://pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="296">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$li-shuai-nan-5" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/li-shuai-nan-5" class="zg-link" title="李帅男">李帅男</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhao-liu-67" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhao-liu-67" class="zg-link" title="赵六">赵六</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$deng-yi-62-4" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/deng-yi-62-4" class="zg-link" title="将荣耀寄于吾身">将荣耀寄于吾身</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2385801" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">唐国强，陈道明，焦晃，李雪健等。<br>你看着像谁就是谁，各取所需，和其光同其尘。<br><br>这是说人类。<br>再说非人类，我想印一头老青牛。<br><br>1.<br>我国自古是以农立国，牛代表了最先进生产力的发展方向，老牛精神也是我们的文化所推崇的。<br><br>2.<br>当年我道老君骑青牛，西出函谷，留下了《道德经》，使我等后辈得以一窥大道。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/70b8cb1727ce0e1579ef6b60abb52636_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="441" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/70b8cb1727ce0e1579ef6b60abb52636_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="441" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/70b8cb1727ce0e1579ef6b60abb52636_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/70b8cb1727ce0e1579ef6b60abb52636_b.jpg"><br>3.<br>光武皇帝刘秀起兵时，因缺少马匹曾骑牛作战取胜，中兴了汉室基业。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/77581650caec9b6a07895001815aa820_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="751" data-rawheight="507" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="751" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/77581650caec9b6a07895001815aa820_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="751" data-rawheight="507" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="751" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/77581650caec9b6a07895001815aa820_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/77581650caec9b6a07895001815aa820_b.jpg"><br>4. <br>印牛的正面，象征昂扬的走势，是牛头。<br>印牛的后面，象征深厚的功力，是牛逼。<br><br>（大家说这个新版货币叫什么名字好）


</div>

</div>
