<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="439">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wang-ye-42-67" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wang-ye-42-67" class="zg-link" title="野望">野望</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$pang-zi-tao" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/pang-zi-tao" class="zg-link" title="胖子饕">胖子饕</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$cai-miao-92" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/cai-miao-92" class="zg-link" title="蔡苗">蔡苗</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2385801" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">就用镜面纸，正常纸币花纹，中间印一块留白，连颜色都不用换。<br><br>对着红色的百元大钞，看见满面红光的自己<br><br>对着绿色的五十元整，看见脸色变绿的自己<br><br>对着黄色的贰拾元整，看见面黄如土的自己<br><br>对着灰色的十元纸币，看见面如死灰的自己<br><br>对着蓝色的五元纸币，看见面色铁青的自己<br><br>对着米色的一元纸币，看见脸色苍白的自己<br><br><br>面对人民币，自己为自己代言！
<a href="/question/25508014/answer/31209639" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
